{"tid":2160082,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 想養隻銀影/英短 應該點做","createTime":"2020-08-16T17:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T22:40:27.000Z","uid":112228,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe238325dd039cfb306954e8063f0cbf9a31f3cd","tid":2160082,"uid":112228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"本人係新手黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直都好想養英短/銀影<br />\n平身prefer領養 做左好多資料蒐集<br />\n但等咗好耐都唔見有英短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過fb自家繁殖/領養群睇 有pm問下 點知又爭啲中招+俾人呃<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日同朋友行咗好多間寵物店睇吓點 返到屋企上網見到好多黑店post 搞到好驚 好多人都話買咗返去之後有貓瘟/皮膚病 有啲直情冇打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但真係好想要一隻銀影 可以點做 <br />\n<br />\n或者大家可唔可以講吓你哋隻貓係點樣得翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131384793a471760fa5a1499190f380aff5ec7c5","tid":2160082,"uid":206178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"養緊銀影 名種貓好難領養架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你等吓有冇朋友貓生bb"},{"pid":"000cfce4dce900db7647707c7bf5034e97ea7a63","tid":2160082,"uid":191118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T18:59:21.000Z","msg":"銀影要領養難d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以搵聲譽好既breeder <br />\n最好可以睇貓睇父母"},{"pid":"5e7a7907b54d05c2c87811ed024f6c7b1c7f1f6b","tid":2160082,"uid":322966,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"本身都想要英/美短，但實在太小機會領養，一有都大把人爭，實輪唔到我。最後緣分下接左隻唐貓（賓士貓）番屋企，已經好幸福。勸你唔好淨係Aim名種，話唔定有隻唐唐同你好來電～加油。"},{"pid":"44cd41924675f103ce27c3b0ef40cb35984f45b2","tid":2160082,"uid":280173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"呢幾日見到LAP 有"},{"pid":"ce5b48a1549ebac999b489c5d6bab564a53d51ae","tid":2160082,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"Lap有幾隻英短，不如你去睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lap.org.hk%2Fadoptcat.aspx&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ee0062f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"e487fd345a7341c8022d691dc7ba8d27d24f8b54","tid":2160082,"uid":178429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"買自家繁殖個重要  <br />\n有清晰既出世相  全家福果隻  飲奶相 <br />\n同埋可以見父母  只要你問呢幾樣野  <br />\n好多妖魔鬼怪原形畢露"},{"pid":"b81b73cc2fd6dea1defdcffff57b5ab5c1cfb762","tid":2160082,"uid":112228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5b48a1549ebac999b489c5d6bab564a53d51ae","tid":2160082,"uid":126057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"Lap有幾隻英短，不如你去睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lap.org.hk%2Fadoptcat.aspx&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ee0062f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"我見有隻英短藍貓 都好可愛 但我想搵下有冇銀影先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0adbecd81d0e9d788e4df4c60dfbe6e5b7627d7","tid":2160082,"uid":112228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e487fd345a7341c8022d691dc7ba8d27d24f8b54","tid":2160082,"uid":178429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"買自家繁殖個重要  <br />\n有清晰既出世相  全家福果隻  飲奶相 <br />\n同埋可以見父母  只要你問呢幾樣野  <br />\n好多妖魔鬼怪原形畢露"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"唔該曬 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035637e82d262a6f05a9cbb6fcda7c94